As per comments in #111 and #127 we should automatically deploy wheels as part of the CI process.
@nicoddemus mentioned that we can do the same as in [`pytest-xdist`](https://github.com/pytest-dev/pytest-xdist/blob/4dc86a1dad8e1924064db32d5b9ea49f2e33c2e1/.travis.yml#L50-L59).

Ideally this is working for the next release!

